        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h2 class="text-light">Mobile App Development</h2>
                <p class="text-light">If you’re looking to extend your marketing efforts or have the next great app concept, we’re ready to bring your ideas to life. We also design HTML 5 mobile apps that are not only functional but also responsive, so you know they’ll work beautifully on just about any mobile screen.</p>
